---
source: crates/mpl-hir/tests/lower.rs
expression: "snapshot(r#\"set custom_unit = \"ms\";\nhttp:request_duration[5m] as latency\n| where service == \"api\" and not status is string\n| map fill::const(0)\n| align to $__interval using avg\n| group by service, region using sum\n| bucket by status to 1m using histogram(\"le\")\n| extend slo = 99.9, matcher = #/api\\/v1/\n| as api_latency\n\"#,)"
---
INPUT:

set custom_unit = "ms";
http:request_duration[5m] as latency
| where service == "api" and not status is string
| map fill::const(0)
| align to $__interval using avg
| group by service, region using sum
| bucket by status to 1m using histogram("le")
| extend slo = 99.9, matcher = #/api\/v1/
| as api_latency

